OL,6,FThe prospect of watching the Coronation
OL,7,Fled to a huge jump in the sales of    
OL,8,Ftelevisions  helped too by the gradual
OL,9,Feasing of postwar austerity and       
OL,10,Frestrictions.                         
OL,12,FAn episode of the much-loved ITV      
OL,13,FSchools series How We Used to Live    
OL,14,Fbroadcast in the early 80s  Your     
OL,15,FUndoubted Queen  interweaved the story
OL,16,Fof Coronation Day with the Hodgkins'  
OL,17,Ffamily getting their first television.
OL,18,F(This edition of the programme can be 
OL,19,Ffound on YouTube.)                    
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television             
OL,22,                                  G3/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
