OL,6,FIt is interesting to contemplate      
OL,7,Fwhether television in Britain would   
OL,8,Fhave taken off quite so rapidly without
OL,9,Fthe boost of the Coronation.          
OL,11,FIt is easy to imagine a more gradual  
OL,12,Fincrease in penetration. Had this     
OL,13,Fhappened, would television have become
OL,14,Fquite such a part of Britain's popular
OL,15,Fculture so early?                     
OL,17,FWithout the rapid increase in sales   
OL,18,Fwould the new ITV companies  which did
OL,19,Fstruggle to begin with in 1955 and 1956
OL,20,F have become quite so lucrative so   
OL,21,Fquickly?                              
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
OL,4,Cdevelopment of television             
OL,22,                                  G4/10
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
