OL,6,FThe Investiture of the Prince of Wales
OL,7,Fin 1969  shown while only BBC Two was
OL,8,Fin colour  was one of the events which
OL,9,Fhighlighted that colour television here
OL,10,Fwas true and natural.                 
OL,12,FThe Mexico Olympics the previous year 
OL,13,Fundoubtedly attracted interest to     
OL,14,Fcolour television but the converted   
OL,15,FNTSC picture quality may not have been
OL,16,Fquite so impressive as the high quality
OL,17,FPAL images.                           
