OL,6,FFour years later, the wedding of      
OL,7,FPrincess Anne gave a big boost to the 
OL,8,Fsale of colour sets which were, by    
OL,9,Fthen, becoming much more affordable.  
OL,11,FIt is also worth noting just how      
OL,12,Fcentral the BBC has been to so many   
OL,13,FRoyal events over the years, even when
OL,14,FITV provided equally good  or arguably
OL,15,Fbetter  coverage.                    
OL,17,FIt highlights the importance of the BBC
OL,18,Fas one of the pillars of national life
OL,19,Fat the moments when we come together. 
OL,3,CThe role of big Royal occasions in the
