OL,6,FThere's been a reminder of that in    
OL,7,Frecent days. In the immediate aftermath
OL,8,Fof The Queen's death the BBC's audience
OL,9,Fwas much higher than normal. Others   
OL,10,Fwere similar to normal or even slightly
OL,11,Fsmaller  this is no reflection of the
OL,12,Fwork of individuals. Some tiny digital
OL,13,Fchannels were completely irrelevant.  
OL,15,FMany writers and commentators have    
OL,16,Fobserved that the passing of the Queen
OL,17,Ftruly marks the end of an era in      
OL,18,FBritish history.                      
