OL,6,FThey have contrasted life in 1952 with
OL,7,Fthe present day and looked at the huge
OL,8,Fcultural, social and economic changes 
OL,9,Fin that time.                         
OL,11,FLet us hope high quality linear       
OL,12,Ftelevision and public service         
OL,13,Fbroadcasting are as important through 
OL,14,Fthe age of King Charles III.          
